RelatedSentence: But ITV have today revealed four alternate showdowns with Tina and the most likely murder suspects ahead of her final scenes , which air from next week .

In all of the exclusive scenes , Tina battles with all four of her enemies on the balcony of the builder 's yard - but only on May 27 , will fans finally get to see the real scene which will ultimately see her plunge to her death on Corrie 's cobbles below .
